                     <title key="work_23010">ساقی‌نامه</title>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_16145304708378611094">Fayyāz̤</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_16145304708378611094">فيّاض</persName>
                     </author>
                     <note>
                        <p>Delhi Persian 1373f.</p>
                        <p>Untitled mas̲navī in the form of an address to the allegorical cupbearer or sāqī traditionally entitled 
                <title key="work_23010">Sāqī'nāmah</title>, by the poet Fayyāz̤ (d. 1072/1661).
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end.</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
